Package: staccuracy
Title: Standardized Accuracy and Other Model Performance Metrics
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Chitu", "Okoli", , "Chitu.Okoli@skema.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5574-7572"))
Language: en-US
Description: Functions for calculating standardized accuracy (staccuracy) based on provided performance metrics. Also functions from some classic performance metrics that are highly recommended (such as MAE, RMSE, and AUCROC) as well as their winsorized versions when applicable.
